,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: Do not curse Satan, rather mention Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Malih reported: A man said, \"I was riding on a mount behind the Prophet, and it stumbled, so I said: May Satan perish!\" The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Do not say: May Satan perish! If you say that, he will swell with pride until he\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23725,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/09\/15\/calmness-allah-haste-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":26683,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Calm: Composure from Allah, haste from Satan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 15, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEquanimity is from Allah, and rushing is from Satan.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 20270 Grade: Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0651\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u0650\u064a \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 20270\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25163,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/08\/14\/waswas-angels-devils\/","url_meta":{"origin":26683,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Waswas: Angels suggest good, devils suggest evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Satan influences the son of Adam and so does the angel. As for the influence of Satan, he threatens evil and denies the truth. As for the influence of the angel, he promises goodness\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33028,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/seek-refuge-entering-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":26683,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from Satan when entering mosque","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the mosque, he would say, \u201cI seek refuge in Allah Almighty, in his noble countenance, and in his everlasting authority from the accursed Satan.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 466 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38541,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/25\/iblees-snout\/","url_meta":{"origin":26683,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Satan: Shaytan withdraws when Allah is remembered","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 25, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu'adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, Satan has a snout like that of a dog positioned over the son of Adam, reminding him of his lusts and his pleasures, bringing him vain hopes and bringing his whisperings to incite doubt\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34606,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/30\/refuge-from-shaytan-kibr\/","url_meta":{"origin":26683,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Arrogance: The Prophet seeks refuge from Satan\u2019s pride","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from the accursed Satan, his madness, his pride, and his poetry.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 808 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u